name: Free wordmarks!
description:
Every day I release a new wordmark! I always use Google Fonts. You're welcome to duplicate them, modify them with your brand name and use them in any free or commercial project. Follow me on Twitter to find out my latest release or request a specific wordmark: https://twitter.com/antimoFM


If you found this useful and want to learn to make these, please check out my Figma course on Gumroad: https://bit.ly/moo-logo
